item.title: Teny
item.description: Teny is a beautiful female Ambilobe panther chameleon who we produced with Tony and Paige. Her sire had nice deep blue bars like his dam sire, Artemis with a clean yellow body like Nugget. Her dam brings a great Tropical Chameleons x Modern Day Dragons YBBB lineage from Tiffany Mallay.
